        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-0577e291-957e-48ca-95f8-b5b00f0b1b78">
                Mr. Woodburn
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0577e291-957e-48ca-95f8-b5b00f0b1b78" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-11/debates/469582f3-632b-4611-9348-e5c7de92cf42/Clause28%E2%80%94(TransactionsDesignedToAvoidLiabilityToTheProfitsTax)#contribution-0577e291-957e-48ca-95f8-b5b00f0b1b78">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Perhaps the hon. and learned Gentleman will clear up the point. Why should profit made in that company not pay its contribution to the State the same as the profit of another company?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
