nes, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Snow, J. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Fraser, Thomas (Hamilton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mack, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sorensen, R. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Freeman, John (Watford)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McKay, John (Wallsend)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Soskice, Rt. Hon. Sir Frank</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Freeman, Peter (Newport)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mackay, R. W. G. (Reading, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Steele, T.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gaitskell, Rt. Hon. H. T. N.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McLeavy, F.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stewart, Michael (Fulham, E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ganley, Mrs. C. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>MacMillan, Malcolm (Western Isles)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stokes, Rt. Hon. R. R.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gibson, C. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McNeil, Rt. Hon. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Strachey, Rt. Hon. J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gilzean, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>MacPherson, Malcolm (Stirling)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Strauss, Rt. Hon. George (Vauxhall)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Glanville, James (Consett)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mainwaring, W. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stross, Dr. Barnett</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gooch, E. G.</td></p><p class