le, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Watkins, T. E.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Henderson, Rt. Hon. Arthur (Tipton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mulley, F. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Webb, Rt. Hon. M. (Bradford, C.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Herbison, Miss M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Murray, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Weitzman, D.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hewitson, Capt. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Nally, W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Walls, Percy (Faversham)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hobson, C. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Neal, Harold (Bolsover)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Weds, William (Walsall)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Holman, P.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Noel-Baker, Rt. Hon. P. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>West, D. G.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Holmes, Horace (Hemsworth)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>O'Brien, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wheatley, Rt. Hon. John (Edmb'gh E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Houghton, D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Oldfield, W. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, Mrs. Eirene (E. Flint)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hoy, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Oliver, G. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, Henry (Derbyshire, N. E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hubbard, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orbach, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <t