<p class="">No. If the first Amendment falls, the others fall with it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-03dbc16e-f9fb-4771-ae06-7c7db51b4a10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
