<div class="content-item" id="contribution-ce19e5b3-bae0-4c7a-90fb-a69dca11a25d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-ce19e5b3-bae0-4c7a-90fb-a69dca11a25d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
