<p class="">could be spending the morning in pleasantâ€”[HON. MEMBERS: "Sit down."] I speak as a Member who has not previously spoken during this sitting. If the Home Secretary disregards the reasonable comfort of the messengers, the police and the women in the Catering Department, he is neglecting his duty as Leader of the House.</p>
