        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-6e95849e-b5d7-4757-8faa-d96bf2d3913f'>
            
<p class="">8.15 a.m.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
