<p class="">Does that not reduce the figures of the profits assessable to Profits Tax?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1129a804-2a5c-42e3-9c89-da7f8c7bd5d3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
