        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-6e339cb9-4238-4c0f-b0c8-45397445fb1b'>
            
<p class="">Amendment negatived.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
