on, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lindgren, G. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Silverman, Sydney (Nelson)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Follick, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lipton, Lt.-Col. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Simmons, C. J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Foot, M. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Logan, D. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Slater, J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Forman, J. C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Longden, Fred (Small Heath)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Smith, Ellis (Stoke, S.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Fraser, Thomas (Hamilton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McAllister, G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Smith, Norman (Nottingham, S.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Freeman, John (Watford)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>MacColl, J. E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Snow, J. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Freeman, Peter (Newport)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McGhee, H. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sorensen, B. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gaitskell, Rt. Hon. H. T. N.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McInnes, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Soskice, Rt. Hon. Sir Frank</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ganley, Mrs. C. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mack, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sparks, J. A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gibson, C. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McKay, John (Wallsen