rien, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>West, D. G.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Holmes, Horace (Hemsworth)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Oldfield, W. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wheatley, Rt. Hon. John (Edinb'gh E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Houghton, D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Oliver, G. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, Mrs. Eirene (E. Flint)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hoy, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orbach, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>While, Henry (Derbyshire, N. E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hubbard, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Padley, W. E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Whiteley, Rt. Hon. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hudson, James (Ealing, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Paling, Rt. Hon. W. (Dearne Valley)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilcock, Group Capt. C. A. B.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hughes, Emrys (S. Ayrshire)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Paling, Will T. (Dewsbury)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilkes, L.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hughes, Hector (Aberdeen, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pannell, T. C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilkins, W. A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hynd, H. (Accrington)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pargiter, G. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Willey, Frederick (Sunderland)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hughes, Moelwyn (Islington, N.)</td></p><p cla