<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-083c1d27-a443-4753-a9c1-e3ee87ce2e62'>
            
<p class="">1.30 p.m.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25">
                Mr. Maudling
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-06-11/debates/469582f3-632b-4611-9348-e5c7de92cf42/Clause28%E2%80%94(TransactionsDesignedToAvoidLiabilityToTheProfitsTax)#contribution-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am afraid I have not made my argument clear to the hon. Gentleman. My point was that in a case like that, where the taxpayer has arranged that the income of company B shall go up at the expense of company A, the Commissioners are entitled to come along and say, "We will nullify the transaction."</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-180d8de0-d16f-4533-ac29-a7822bb77c25" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
