ydon, W.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Langford-Holt, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orr, Capt. L. P. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thorneycroft, Peter (Monmouth)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Leather, E. H. C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orr-Ewing, Charles Ian (Hendon, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thornton-Kemsley, Col. C. N.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Legge-Bourke, Maj. E. A. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orr-Ewing, Ian L. (Weston-super-Mare)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thorp, Brig. R. A. F.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lennox-Boyd, A. T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Osborne, C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Tilney, John</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lindsay, Martin</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Peake, Rt. Hon. O.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Turner, H. F. L.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Linstead, H. N.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Perkins, W. R. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Turton, R. H.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Llewellyn, D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Peto, Brig. C. H. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Vane, W. M. F.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lloyd, Rt. Hn. Geoffrey (King's Norton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pickthorn, K.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Vaughan-Morgan, J. K.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lloyd, Maj. Guy (Renfrew, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pitman, I. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> 