        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-491c45b3-78cd-44a5-8d15-4bba69eb6f7d'>
            
<p class="">2.45 p.m.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
