iams, Rt. Hon. Thomas (Don V'lly)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Morrison, Rt. Hon. H. (Lewisham, S.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Smith, Ellis (Stoke, S.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Williams, W. T. (Hammersmith, S.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mort, D. L.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Smith, Norman (Nottingham, S.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilson, Rt. Hon. Harold (Huyton)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Moyle, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Snow, J. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterbottom, Ian (Nottingham, C.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mulley, F. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sorensen, R. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterbottom, Richard (Brightside)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Murray, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Soskice, Rt. Hon. Sir Frank</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wise, F. J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Nally, W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Sparks, J. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Woodburn, Rt. Hon. A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Neal, Harold (Bolsover)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Steele, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Woods, Rev. G. S.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Noel-Baker, Rt. Hon. P. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stewart, Michael (Fulham, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wyatt, W. L.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>O'Brien, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stokes, Rt. Hon. R. R</td></p>